{"tid":984663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太陽花時警察毆打民眾　隨後　台灣公眾義憤圍警局　局長道歉請辭","createTime":"2019-01-17T03:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T03:40:51.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"65a76404e86f48b279ba3d345b9c388700b90f55","tid":984663,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.taiwanjustice.net/2014/04/11/上千民眾包圍-方仰寧：口頭請辭接受調查-◎新頭殼/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwanjustice.net%2F2014%2F04%2F11%2F%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%83%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%B0%E5%AF%A7%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%A3%E9%A0%AD%E8%AB%8B%E8%BE%AD%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E2%97%8E%E6%96%B0%E9%A0%AD%E6%AE%BC%2F&d=wupA0mMK9VTR1jnO51Ll3hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=71cd3e06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwanjustice.net/2014/04/11/上千民眾包圍-方仰寧：口頭請辭接受調查-◎新頭殼/</a><br />\n<br />\n上千名網友因為不滿中正一分局今(11)日清晨在立法院外驅離「公投護台灣聯盟」的行動，傍晚6點包圍分局嗆聲，晚間10點10分左右，分局長方仰寧3度 出面面對場外民眾，他面色凝重的宣布，「早上執行勤務的過程，你們大家都不能接受，我非常抱歉！」「我口頭請辭、接受調查」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20140411/345522.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20140411%2F345522.htm&d=wupA0mMK9VTR1jnO51Ll3hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f2110aef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20140411/345522.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n面對群眾包圍台北市中正一分局，分局長方仰寧11日晚上10時多再步出分局發言，「早上執行過程，使得大家不能接受，我誠懇地道歉。」他表示自己口頭請辭接受調查。"}]}